Keep up to date with your favourite daily value and best bet horse racing tips. Click here for more horse racing news, profiles and much more, only in The Citizen. KENILWORTH BEST BET RACE 4 NO 3 AENEAS WIN This is not an easy card and almost every race is competitive. The positive aspect is that there is always some decent value. Candice Bass-Robinson saddles Aeneas who is the best-weighted runner, is well drawn at No 4 and has Aldo Domeyer up. VALUE BET RACE 7 SWINGERS: BOX 2-MISS GREENLIGHT 3-PERFECT TRUST AND 9-BONIKA This is a very open race and if one catches a Swinger it will pay well. This is case of combining decent form with good jockeys and trainers. In this case they are Louis Mxothwa, Richard Fourie and Greg Cheyne on horses trained by Brett Crawford, Eric Sands and Glen Kotzen respectively .